 lifestyle<\/p>"}},"52bfd24f-8f46-4a4a-a0a9-c33916419e47":{"type":"faq","settings":{"faq-ques":"How long does it take to feel the effects?","faq-content":"<p>ARK Drops provide an instant kick that leaves you feeling more motivated and energized. The long-term benefits typically occur after using ARK Drops for 10 days.<\/p>"}},"faq_3ydaQj":{"type":"faq","settings":{"faq-ques":"Does Ark drop contain caffeine ?","faq-content":"<p>No, ARK Drops does not contain caffeine.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["8a01a5ba-a1ec-432a-9ab5-e8b7a7bb31a0","4a43d308-0fc8-4462-9127-042d68fc8077","d37333f3-812c-4def-9afc-b41ea9840783","52bfd24f-8f46-4a4a-a0a9-c33916419e47","faq_3ydaQj"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"title":"<strong>Questions? We’ve Got You Covered<\/strong>","bg-faq-color":"#ffffff","faq-ques-color":"#000000"}},"170664101886ef77cd":{"type":"apps","settings":{"include_margins":true}}},"order":["main","4536657b-07aa-4787-922f-be0de52afe9c","image_banner_TmDkKP","image_banner_pThAQy","image_banner_8aGdqz","image_banner_eRYBMt","multicolumn_j4GrD4","image_banner_aidfLt","6c377b2f-41b5-4a6c-a394-18f152fdfdba","dd089b3d-72d7-4ca9-a99f-2f8322aec5f4","rich_text_iHkxtB","8bb65be9-da27-4363-93a6-7ef4f50d53a3","668dc45f-0738-4cce-beb7-38d94901a455","related-products","164451a9-0f1f-4479-9109-ebc7c6e5542c","170664101886ef77cd"]}